<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.7">
<l>paṇṇiṉiṉ moḻiyāḻna rampilpeṟ ṟapālai yākiyiṅ kēpukunteṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇumneñ cumvāyumi ṭaṅkoṇṭāṉ koṇṭapiṉma ṟaiyōr maṉantaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>viṇṇuḷār perumāṉai yemmāṉai vīṅkunīr makaramti ḷaikkumkaṭal</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṉmā maṇivaṇṇa ṉemmaṇṇal vaṇṇamē yaṉṟivāyu raiyātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Resembling the ‘desert’ [mood] produced on lute strings</l>
<l rend="indent">with sweet sounds in music, entering here,</l>
<l>He took [his] place in my eyes, heart, and mouth; after [that],</l>
<l rend="indent">without the beauty of the great lord of those in heaven</l>
<l>[Who is] in the minds of Vedic experts, our lord, the one the hue of the sea</l>
<l rend="indent">where makaras abound in swelling waters,</l>
<l>The dark jewel-hued lord, my great lord, [my] mouth does not speak.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
